"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"This is a summary article on Heros of Mavia.\\nIt also includes the latest version of the Whitelist numbers. \\n Also use discord for updates!\\n\\n[https://discord.gg/JT8SJna4](https://discord.gg/JT8SJna4)\\n\\n## 1. What’s Mavia ?\\n\\nMavia is a blockchain game featuring \\\"blockchain battles\\\". \\n Heroes of Mavia offers **AAA-quality graphics and cutting-edge features** never before seen on GameFi.\\nIn addition, NFT consists of three elements: **bases, heroes, and stone statues**, all of which can be **upgraded**.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/pnE-phiXfYxFZiQEEmNjh.png?height=388&width=1120)\\n\\n## 2. What are the features of Mavia?\\n\\n### Token\\n\\nMavia uses a **dual token model**. Here are the features of the tokens! \\n ***1. $Mavia is a token for buying and selling game NFTs.  \\n 2.$RUBY is a token for upgrading heroes, etc.***\\n\\n$RUBY token is used to upgrade heroes, etc.  \\n And $RUBY token is burned, so there is deflationary pressure. But don't worry, we are doing **a lot of economic model simulation**s for $RUBY to prevent P2E from going bankrupt.\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/LmPdw3pig9ZeHHMVLxqSv.png?height=360&width=680)\\n\\n### Game\\n\\nHeros of Mavia represents one world in the game. Battles, economy, and money are the history that we humans have been going through. It's a great game to experience these histories.  \\n In addition, Heros of Mavia has the following features. \\n  \\n ***1.Inspired by Axie and Clash of Clans Earn tokens by defeating enemies and defending your base . \\n 2.The blockchain is built on Ethereum (Arbitrum).  \\n 3.These are by far the best of the other blockchain games.***\\n\\n**There's no better game than this!**\\n\\nClick here for details：\\n\\n[https://medium.com/heroes-of-mavia/introducing-mavia-aaa-blockchain-base-builder-strategy-game-f2bae820a444](https://medium.com/heroes-of-mavia/introducing-mavia-aaa-blockchain-base-builder-strategy-game-f2bae820a444)\\n\\n## 3. Mavia Whitelist\\n\\nA summary of the Mavia whitelist is below. Here is the latest version.\\n\\n1\\\\.Total number of **whitelists is 3k**. \\n 2.**Public sale is 1k.** \\n 3.**A total of 4k** land NFTs are available. \\n  \\n There are **four whitelist** pools.  \\n ***1. Content Creators : 900 + 450 Entry \\n 2. Community Engagement : 700 + 350 Entry \\n 3. Art and Memes : 300 + 150 Entry \\n 4. Influencers : 100 + 50 Entry***\\n\\n**We must not miss this opportunity! \\n  \\n **Click here for details：\\n\\n[https://medium.com/heroes-of-mavia/mavia-announcement-whitelist-community-updates-73316b3b64eb](https://medium.com/heroes-of-mavia/mavia-announcement-whitelist-community-updates-73316b3b64eb)\\n\\n**That's all.\\nLet's all support the Mavia!**\\n\\n** \\n  \\n Mavia’s Social**  \\n Web: [https://mavia.com](https://t.co/iaJLdirybO)  \\n Discord: \\n\\n[https://discord.gg/JT8SJna4](https://discord.gg/JT8SJna4)\\n\\n \\n Medium: [https://medium.com/heroes-of-mavia](https://t.co/wkVX948Lof)  \\n Game Deck: [https://mavia.com/game_deck.pdf](https://t.co/uonUCce8m7) \\n  \\n  \\n Writter’s Social \\n Twiiter:\\n\\n[https://twitter.com/learning_invest](https://twitter.com/learning_invest)\\n\\n \\n \",\"timestamp\":1642296208,\"title\":\"Introduction to Mavia \\nBlockchain Based Builder Game\"},\"digest\":\"Tmx23EADIlQUHOCzCvXYF_j9j5PVzay_A4t17Uc-X5M\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x6309Dac268FF8f19A1a073e24F4126B44Ef5B76C\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"ICk-wgLDFu-UZogon8lp6wFF_kFXdqLjDE_r95Si_oA\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"Le8zclTpX5WERoILRnz8WE7R8etfsg8VgSqTAzKVgXc\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"CjmRY_0AqiBiubnsbkjR8U_7gmgjSQysht6AHhYGc4Je7h6Q0nQB-oKTU6AGAewsKkcdzaDCmtKSy-vUHuF3og\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x8e217f526ea615210ea36731af25ee9854ab18c859c04bf66d346480fb2afb5552a9881f7beeba57265a250e646eddf0ade4c5483b20bb9b490